<lb n="0229b13"/>訶喝羅闍<note place="inline">十三</note>綺槃達伽寫<note place="inline">十四</note>哆羅摩車都<note place="inline">十
<lb n="0229b14"/>五</note>娑婆訶</p>
<lb n="0229b15"/><p>行者上下衣服並淨潔。一上廁一洗浴。白月
<lb n="0229b16"/>十五日起首。對像前誦&CB00057;滿十萬遍訖。然後
<lb n="0229b17"/>取香復塗壇上。復設種種飲食。行者取薰陸
<lb n="0229b18"/>香一百八枚。各&CB00057;一遍投著火中。天王即現。</p>
<lb n="0229b19"/><p>又法行者若欲得。曷羅闍所愛敬者。取赤小
<lb n="0229b20"/>豆。一&CB00057;一遍投火中燒。如是滿一百八遍。
<lb n="0229b21"/>其曷羅闍即遣人喚來極急。</p><p place="inline">又法若欲得大
<lb n="0229b22"/>官愛敬者。取白芥子一&CB00057;一遍投火中。如是
<lb n="0229b23"/>滿一百八遍。即自來敬仰大喜。</p><p place="inline">又法若欲遠
<lb n="0229b24"/>行。&CB00057;穀木<note n="0229006" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">柱＝拄&M062403;【原】，杖&M062303;&M062485;【原】</note><note n="0229006" resp="CBETA" type="mod">柱＝拄&M062403;【原】，＝杖&M062303;【原】，＝杖&M062485;【原】</note><app n="0229006"><lem><sic corr="杖" resp="【原】">柱</sic></lem><rdg wit="【Ａ】" resp="【原】">拄</rdg><rdg wit="【Ｂ】" resp="【原】">杖</rdg></app>。行一切難更無著障礙。</p><p place="inline">又法
<lb n="0229b25"/>若欲人愛敬。取苦<note n="0229007" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">練＝楝&M062403;【原】＊</note><app n="0229007"><lem>練</lem><rdg wit="【Ａ】" resp="【原】">楝</rdg></app><note n="0229008" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">子＝木&M062303;【原】</note><app n="0229008"><lem>子</lem><rdg wit="【Ｂ】" resp="【原】">木</rdg></app>一百八顆。一&CB00057;一
<lb n="0229b26"/>遍投火中燒之。如是一切人愛敬&CB00057;師如親
<lb n="0229b27"/>父母。悉滿心所願。</p><p place="inline">又法若欲怨家遠相&CB00230;
<lb n="0229b28"/>者。取苦<app type="＊" source="0229007"><lem>練</lem><rdg resp="【原】" wit="【Ａ】">楝</rdg></app>子百八顆。一&CB00057;一遍投火中燒。
<lb n="0229b29"/>其人即遠行不在。</p><p place="inline">又法若欲令人降伏。稱
<pb ed="T" id="T21.1249.0229c" n="0229c"/>
<lb n="0229c01"/>前人姓名。&CB00057;酪一百八遍燒之。</p><p place="inline">又法欲令
<lb n="0229c02"/>自在威光者。&CB00057;墨塗額上。一切見者無不愛
<lb n="0229c03"/>仰。</p><p place="inline">又法若有鬼病心痛者。&CB00057;石榴華汁飲
<lb n="0229c04"/>之即差。</p><p place="inline">又法若患野狐鬼魅。&CB00057;楊枝打病
<lb n="0229c05"/>者即差。</p><p place="inline">又法若患一切風。&CB00057;蘇二十一遍
<lb n="0229c06"/>食之即差。</p><p place="inline">又法若患<note n="0229009" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">虐＝瘧&M062403;【原】</note><app n="0229009"><lem>虐</lem><rdg wit="【Ａ】" resp="【原】">瘧</rdg></app>病者&CB00057;楊柳枝二
<lb n="0229c07"/>十一遍。令打病人即差。</p><p place="inline">又法患狂言鬼語。
<lb n="0229c08"/>&CB00057;水令服之即差。</p><p place="inline">又法若患心痛。&CB00057;黃土塗
<lb n="0229c09"/>之。</p><p place="inline">若患一切鬼病者。&CB00057;石榴杖百八遍。打
<lb n="0229c10"/>病人即差。</p><p place="inline"><note n="0229010" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">原&M062303;本註云智明曰此印出吠室囉末那軌之畢</note>作印法。二小指相鉤。二無名指
<lb n="0229c11"/>向外直&CB00594;。二中指二頭指反相叉。二大母指
<lb n="0229c12"/>向外直&CB00594;。手掌相背是<note place="inline">以上所說<note n="0229011" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔二〕&M062303;－&M062485;【原】</note><note n="0229011" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔二〕&M062303;－【原】，〔二〕－&M062485;【原】</note><app n="0229011"><lem><sic corr="＆lac；" resp="【原】">二</sic></lem><rdg wit="【Ｂ】" resp="【原】">&lac;</rdg></app>法中皆用此印</note>誦此真
<lb n="0229c13"/>言數滿。即誦使者真言七遍。又誦八天真言
<lb n="0229c14"/>各三遍。</p>
<lb n="0229c15"/><p>毘沙門天王使者&CB00057;</p>
<lb n="0229c16"/><p type="dharani">娜謨吠失羅<note place="inline">二合</note><note n="0229012" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">原&M062303;本註云&CB00425;同軌作拔</note>&CB00425;那耶摩訶藥叉栖那&CB00425;多
<lb n="0229c17"/>耶唵薩婆羯囉<note place="inline">二合</note>那尾數陀抳薩&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合</note>訶<note place="inline">增
<lb n="0229c18"/>益</note></p>
<lb n="0229c19"/><p type="dharani">娜莫三<note place="inline">去</note>曼多勃馱<note place="inline">引</note>喃<note place="inline">上引一</note>阿&CB00425;囉<note place="inline">二合</note>底<note place="inline">丁以反</note>
<lb n="0229c20"/>賀多捨<note place="inline">引</note>娑曩<note place="inline">引</note>南<note place="inline">二</note>唵<note place="inline">引</note>&CB00230;&CB00230;佉<note place="inline">去引</note>呬佉呬
<lb n="0229c21"/><note place="inline"><note n="0229013" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">聲＝馨&M062303;&M062485;【原】，磬&M062303;&M062485;【原】</note>聲異反上同三</note>吽<note place="inline">引</note>吽<note place="inline">引</note>入&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合</note>&CB00256;入&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合</note>&CB00256;<note place="inline">四</note>&CB00425;
<lb n="0229c22"/>囉<note place="inline">二合</note>入&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合</note>&CB00256;&CB00425;囉<note place="inline">二合</note>入&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合</note>&CB00256;<note place="inline">五</note>底瑟
<lb n="0229c23"/>奼<note place="inline">二合</note>底瑟吒<note place="inline">二合六</note>瑟置哩<note place="inline">三合引七</note>娑發吒<note place="inline">半音呼</note>娑發
<lb n="0229c24"/>吒<note place="inline">半音</note>娑&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合</note>訶<note place="inline">息災</note>尾沙野娑&CB00085;鉻<note place="inline">又云波底</note>唵藥
<lb n="0229c25"/>叉布彈那吽因陀羅弊薩&CB00085;賀毘<note n="0229014" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">沙＝裟&M062303;&M062485;【原】</note><note n="0229014" resp="CBETA" type="mod">沙＝裟&M062303;【原】，＝裟&M062485;【原】</note><app n="0229014"><lem><sic corr="裟" resp="【原】">沙</sic></lem><rdg wit="【Ｂ】" resp="【原】">裟</rdg></app>遮那娑
<lb n="0229c26"/>&CB00085;賀<note place="inline">降伏陀彌使者</note></p>
<lb n="0229c27"/><p>誦此真言用此契。二手作拳直&CB00594;二食指。次
<lb n="0229c28"/>開二大母指。次右食指超左食指背上入掌
<lb n="0229c29"/>中。以<note n="0229015" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">原&M062303;本註云智明曰左食指之下恐有脫超右食指背上入掌中九字若不然則難二頭出外</note>左食指入右掌中。次二大母指。左把
<pb ed="T" id="T21.1249.0230a" n="0230a"/>
<lb n="0230a01"/>右食<note n="0230001" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">指＋（右把左食指）【原】</note><app n="0230001"><lem>指</lem><rdg wit="【原】" resp="Taisho">指右把左食指</rdg></app>。二頭出外。</p>
<lb n="0230a02"/><p>八大天王。摩尼跋陀羅　布嚕娜跋陀羅
<lb n="0230a03"/>　半只迦　娑多祁里　醯摩&CB00085;多　毘灑迦
<lb n="0230a04"/>　阿陀&CB00085;迦　半灑&CB00256;</p>
<lb n="0230a05"/><juan fun="close" n="001"><jhead>毘沙門儀軌</jhead></juan>
<lb n="0230a06"/><p type="W">八家錄云。毘沙門天王儀軌一卷睿。此軌
<lb n="0230a07"/>以智積院慈順僧正御本。當山愛染院大
<lb n="0230a08"/>宣等挍合。予亦挍訂而壽梓。</p>
<lb n="0230a09"/><p type="W">亨和改元辛酉秋八月　豐山僧快道誌</p>
<lb n="0230a10"/><p type="W">　一挍加筆了　　　　　　　　慈順</p>
<lb n="0230a11"/><p type="W">　文政三年庚辰八月二十八日以秀陽闍
<lb n="0230a12"/>梨本挍合之了　　　　　　　龍肝</p>
<lb n="0230a13"/><p type="W">　同　四年辛巳九月二十三日以板橋日
<lb n="0230a14"/>曜寺本再挍之了<note place="inline">朱注是也</note>　　　　　龍肝</p></div1>
